1. About me

Hi, I’m Joseph, a self-taught data analyst from Morocco inspired by Hans Rosling’s work.
My hands-on experience in data scraping, analysis, and visualization fuels my innovative thinking—though I’d benefit from structured onboarding to align with team standards.

I’m available to work remotely at any time, fully flexible across time zones. I’m happy to start as a free intern, either part-time or full-time, to contribute and learn. Beyond the role, I hope to build meaningful, lasting connections with teammates.

Feel free to reach me at joseph.ergo@proton.me
